= quick info =
Please turn you browser to http://www.buzztard.org to learn what this project
is about. Buzztard is free software and distributed under the LGPL.

= intro =
This module provide a set of buzzmachines that have been released as open source.
They can be used via bml library or in all gstreamer app via bml+gstbml.

= installing locally =
You can install this module locally too.
Use following option for ./autogen.sh or ./configure
  --prefix=$HOME/buzztard/

Add the path to the BML_PATH env var:
  export BML_PATH=$HOME/buzztard/lib/Gear:$HOME/buzztard/lib/Gear/Effects:\
    $HOME/buzztard/lib/Gear/Generators

The native one will be installed to $prefix/lib/Gear right now.

